WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:07.396
This is the science of SilverStone. The stone at the heart of every Magppie Wellness Kitchen.

2
00:00:09.196 --> 00:00:16.924
Magppie Wellness Kitchens are made entirely from our patented sanitised stone. Zero percent wood.

3
00:00:18.724 --> 00:00:25.348
That means no trees are cut, and no harmful toxins like formaldehyde are released into your home.

4
00:00:27.148 --> 00:00:35.524
The stone contains real silver and copper nano-particles, making your kitchen naturally anti-bacterial and anti-fungal.

5
00:00:37.324 --> 00:00:49.156
It is termite-proof, waterproof, and fire-safe. And it comes with a twenty-five year unconditional guarantee, plus twenty-five complimentary annual services.

6
00:00:50.956 --> 00:01:01.276
So, what is SilverStone? It is our patented wellness stone. We take porcelain clay, and heat it to thirteen hundred degrees Celsius.

7
00:01:03.076 --> 00:01:12.220
Then we infuse it with silver and copper nano-particles. This makes it anti-bacterial, anti-fungal, and non-porous.

8
00:01:14.020 --> 00:01:24.172
It is stain-proof, scratch-resistant, and impact-resistant. And it is one hundred percent food-grade. You can eat directly off it.

9
00:01:25.972 --> 00:01:30.076
It is stronger than granite, and more elegant than marble.

10
00:01:31.876 --> 00:01:37.108
And because it is engineered, not mined, it does not harm the environment.

11
00:01:38.908 --> 00:01:45.700
Remember the key phrase. It looks like a stone, but it does not behave like a regular stone.

12
00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:52.324
SilverStone. The science inside every Wellness Kitchen.

